---
import Base from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
const updated = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-ZA', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' });
const SUPPORT = 'info@landcruisersa.co.za';
---

<Base
  title="Terms & Conditions — Land Cruiser SA"
  description="The terms governing your use of Land Cruiser SA — our listings, market data, valuation estimates and guides."
>
  <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 py-12 md:py-16 prose-custom">
    <h1 class="font-heading font-bold uppercase text-3xl md:text-4xl text-[#111] leading-none">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-2">Last updated {updated}</p>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-7 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
      <p>These terms govern your use of <strong>landcruisersa.co.za</strong> (the "site"), operated by <strong>Land Cruiser SA</strong> ("we", "us"). By using the site you agree to them. If you do not agree, please don't use the site.</p>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold uppercase text-lg text-[#111] mb-2">What we are</h2>
        <p>Land Cruiser SA is an independent information and listings platform for the South African Toyota Land Cruiser market. We aggregate vehicle listings from third-party platforms, publish market data and guides, and provide tools such as our valuation estimator. We are <strong>not</strong> a dealership, broker, finance provider or insurer, and we are not affiliated with Toyota.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold uppercase text-lg text-[#111] mb-2">Listings &amp; aggregated content</h2>
        <p>Many listings are aggregated from third-party sources and link back to the original platform. We don't own, inspect or warrant these vehicles, and we can't guarantee that any listing's price, specification, availability or images are accurate or current. Always verify details directly with the seller or source platform before acting.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold uppercase text-lg text-[#111] mb-2">Valuations &amp; market data</h2>
        <p>Our valuation estimates and market figures are <strong>indicative only</strong> — generated from observed asking prices of comparable listings, not confirmed sale prices. They are not a physical-inspection, finance or insurance valuation, and should not be relied on as a guarantee of any vehicle's worth. Use them as a starting point, not financial advice.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold uppercase text-lg text-[#111] mb-2">Submitting a listing or enquiry</h2>
        <p>If you submit a vehicle or contact us, you confirm the information you provide is accurate and that you're entitled to share it. We may decline, edit or remove any submission at our discretion. How we handle your personal details is set out in our <a href="/privacy-policy/" class="text-[#D4881A] font-semibold">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold uppercase text-lg text-[#111] mb-2">Third-party links &amp; partners</h2>
        <p>The site links to third-party websites, sellers and partners. We're not responsible for their content, products, services or practices, and a link is not an endorsement. Any dealings you have with them are between you and them.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold uppercase text-lg text-[#111] mb-2">Intellectual property</h2>
        <p>Our original content — guides, market data, design and branding — belongs to Land Cruiser SA. You may share and link to it, but you may not republish or scrape it at scale without our written permission.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold uppercase text-lg text-[#111] mb-2">Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>The site is provided "as is". To the extent permitted by law, we're not liable for any loss arising from your use of the site, reliance on its content or estimates, or any third-party listing or transaction.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold uppercase text-lg text-[#111] mb-2">Changes</h2>
        <p>We may update these terms from time to time; the "last updated" date above reflects the current version. These terms are governed by the laws of the Republic of South Africa.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold uppercase text-lg text-[#111] mb-2">Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about these terms? Email us at <a href={`mailto:${SUPPORT}`} class="text-[#D4881A] font-semibold">{SUPPORT}</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
